HAPPY 25TH ANNIVERSARY BARRY’S!!!! From it’s humble yet life changing beginnings in 1998 until 2023, Barry’s (Bootcamp, formerly known as) has stayed true to hard work, community, and innovation all while having fun. I didn’t join this amazing company until 2006 & have been so proud to be part of it and it’s incredible evolution. Forever grateful to @joeygonzalez @rachelcoxton @johnmum22 and @barryscares for creating/growing this company and allowing me to experience this journey where we’ve all forged bonds with clients and employees in and out of the red room. Thank you also to the numerous clients over the years that have made @barrys what it is today! Cheers to another 25 years and beyond!!! ✌️❤️💪 #barrys #barrys25daychallenge #bestworkoutintheworld #barrys25thbirthday #workhardandbenicetopeople
